OL,3,CNHS clinical support staff end strike
OL,4,Caction over backdated pay
OL,6,FStrikes at two hospitals on the Wirral
OL,7,Fhave come to an end after support
OL,8,Fworkers secured back pay and grading.
OL,10,FThe union Unison said clinical support
OL,11,Fworkers (CSWs) at Wirral University
OL,12,FTeaching Hospital NHS Foundation Trust
OL,13,Fhave agreed a deal with the trust that
OL,14,Fshould see more than 600 workers
OL,15,Freceive a wage rise and back pay to
OL,16,FApril 2018.
