OL,6,FUnions said clinical support workers
OL,7,Fon band 2 of the NHS's Agenda for
OL,8,FChange pay scale should only be
OL,9,Fproviding personal care such as
OL,10,Fbathing and feeding, but some of the
OL,11,FCSWs had been routinely undertaking
OL,12,Fclinical tasks, such as taking and
OL,13,Fmonitoring blood, performing
OL,14,Felectrocardiogram tests and inserting
OL,15,Fcannulas, for many years.
OL,17,FAccording to NHS guidance, staff
OL,18,Fperforming these duties should be on
OL,19,Fsalary band 3, which is nearly #2,000
OL,20,Fa year more.
