OL,4,Caction over backdated pay
OL,6,FPresented with the latest offer, this
OL,7,Fweek the workers voted to accept,
OL,8,Fbringing the long-running dispute to
OL,9,Fan end.
OL,11,FThe new deal is the latest North West
OL,12,Fcampaign to ensure clinical support
OL,13,Fworkers and healthcare assistants are
OL,14,Fpaid fairly.
OL,16,FIn the past six months, Warrington and
OL,17,FHalton, East Cheshire and Mid Cheshire
OL,18,Ftrusts joined seven other NHS trusts
OL,19,Fin Greater Manchester by moving
OL,20,Fworkers to the higher rate and
OL,21,Fbackdating their pay to April 2018.
