OL,6,FUNISON North West regional organiser
OL,7,FDavid McKnight said: "For far too
OL,8,Flong, these workers haven't been
OL,9,Ffairly paid.
OL,11,F"They're relieved the trust has
OL,12,Ffinally agreed to do the right thing
OL,13,Fand recognise their hard work.
OL,15,F"Wirral's clinical support workers are
OL,16,Fcompletely dedicated to serving the
OL,17,Flocal community but among the lowest
OL,18,Fpaid staff in the NHS.
