OL,6,F"All they ever asked is for their pay
OL,7,Fto reflect the jobs they were carrying
OL,8,Fout.
OL,10,F"It's a shame it took so long for the
OL,11,Ftrust to make an offer that recognised
OL,12,Ftheir value.
OL,14,F"Nobody wants to take strike action
OL,15,Fbut these workers were determined to
OL,16,Fget justice.
