OL,6,F"Now this has been settled, it will
OL,7,Fleave a legacy of hundreds of fairly
OL,8,Fpaid jobs for future generations of
OL,9,FNHS workers serving the people of the
OL,10,FWirral."
OL,12,FA Wirral University Teaching Hospital
OL,13,Fspokesperson said:
OL,15,F"We have been committed throughout to
OL,16,Freaching an agreement with UNISON.
OL,18,F"We made a pledge to ensure that
OL,19,Fworkers are paid for the work that
OL,20,Fthey undertake and we are glad we have
OL,21,Fnow been able to reach an agreement."
