OL,3,CNHS clinical support staff end strike
OL,4,Caction over backdated pay
OL,6,FThe strikes began on 31 August 2023
OL,7,Fand the last day of strike action was
OL,8,Fon February 8.
OL,10,FThere was a pause in November
OL,11,Ffollowing an agreement between the
OL,12,Ftrust and the union on the date
OL,13,Faffected staff should benefit from
OL,14,Fbackpay, but workers resumed striking
OL,15,Fafter a disagreement over the number
OL,16,Fof people entitled to back pay and
OL,17,Fregrading.
